Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:13.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&\4c&HFFFFFF&\an8\4a&H78&\fad(370,550)}こんな私がいたなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:13.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&\4c&HFFFFFF&\4a&H78&\fad(370,550)}原来还有这样的我存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&\4c&HFFFFFF&\an8\4a&H78&\fad(370,550)}始まった物语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&\4c&HFFFFFF&\4a&H78&\fad(370,550)}故事才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:35.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&\4c&HFFFFFF&\an8\4a&H78&\fad(370,550)}最初の1ページには　风の中に立つ私がいる
